'''Z-Library'''（簡稱'''z-lib'''，前身為'''BookFinder'''）是一個[[影子圖書館|影子圖書館]]和[[檔案分享|檔案分享]]計劃，用戶可在此一網站上下載期刊文章以及各種類型的書籍。根據Z-Library的說法，截至2022年6月12日，其共收錄了10,456,034本書和84,837,646篇文章<ref>{{cite web |title=Z-Library |url=https://z-lib.org |access-date=2021-05-14 |archive-date=2021-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210401181020/https://z-lib.org/ }}</ref>。Z-Library在其電子書搜尋頁面上宣稱自己是「全球最大的數字圖書館」<ref>{{cite web|title=数字图书馆。搜索书籍。免费下载书籍|url=https://zh.b-ok.global/|access-date=2020-02-13|work=Z-Library|archive-date=2021-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210207024325/https://zh.b-ok.global/}}</ref>，並在文章搜尋頁面上稱自身是「全球最大的科學文章儲存庫」<ref>{{cite web|title=数字图书馆。搜索书籍。免费下载书籍|url=https://zh.booksc.org|access-date=2020-02-13|work=Z-Library|archive-date=2021-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210605084936/https://zh.booksc.org/}}</ref>。它是[[創世紀圖書館|創世紀圖書館計劃]]的一部分<ref name="European Commission">{{cite web|title=COMMISSION STAFF WORKING DOCUMENT Counterfeit and Piracy Watch List|url=https://trade.ec.europa.eu/doclib/docs/2020/december/tradoc_159183.pdf|work=European Commission|accessdate=2021-05-14|date=2020-12-14|archive-date=2021-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609115327/https://trade.ec.europa.eu/doclib/docs/2020/december/tradoc_159183.pdf}}</ref>{{rp|30}}。

== 歷史 ==
項目頁面的頁尾寫有「自2009年起提供免费[[電子書|電子书]]」的字句<ref>{{cite web |title=Z-Library |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009125151/https://b-ok.cc/ |access-date=2020-10-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Z-Library |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016095631/https://booksc.org/ |access-date=2020-10-16}}</ref>。Z-Library跟[[Sci-Hub|Sci-Hub]]和[[创世纪图书馆|创世纪图书馆]]一樣，同是相對較著名的影子圖書館，出版商和政府组织在處理反盜版事宜時，通常會把這三個項目歸類為同一類。英國組織{{link-en|出版者協會|The Publishers Association}}曾嘗試要求當地的[[ISP|ISP]]封鎖Z-Library<ref>{{cite web |title=High Court Orders UK ISPs to Block eBook Sites |url=https://torrentfreak.com/high-court-orders-uk-isps-to-block-ebook-sites-150527/ |website=TorrentFreak |language=en |access-date=2021-02-13 |archive-date=2021-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210507130353/https://torrentfreak.com/high-court-orders-uk-isps-to-block-ebook-sites-150527/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=UK Piracy Blocklist Quietly Expands With Proxy Sites |url=https://torrentfreak.com/uk-piracy-blocklist-quietly-expands-with-proxy-sites-150714/ |website=TorrentFreak |language=en |access-date=2021-02-13 |archive-date=2021-05-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210525011330/https://torrentfreak.com/uk-piracy-blocklist-quietly-expands-with-proxy-sites-150714/ }}</ref>。

2015年底，出版商[[愛思唯爾|愛思唯爾]]在法院上要求bookfi.org的註冊商查封該網站域名一事取得成功<ref>{{cite web |title=Court Orders Shutdown of Libgen, Bookfi and Sci-Hub |url=https://torrentfreak.com/court-orders-shutdown-of-libgen-bookfi-and-sci-hub-151102/ |website=TorrentFreak |language=en |access-date=2021-02-13 |archive-date=2020-05-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200504210607/https://torrentfreak.com/court-orders-shutdown-of-libgen-bookfi-and-sci-hub-151102/ }}</ref>。

2017年，美國政府在「声名狼藉的」市場報告中提到了Bookfi.org、booksc.org、b-ok.org<ref>{{cite web |title=2017 Out-of-Cycle Review of Notorious Markets |url=https://ustr.gov/sites/default/files/files/Press/Reports/2017%20Notorious%20Markets%20List%201.11.18.pdf |publisher=Office of the United States Trade Representative |access-date=2020-10-16 |date=2017-08-16 |archive-date=2020-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200304001726/https://ustr.gov/sites/default/files/files/Press/Reports/2017%20Notorious%20Markets%20List%201.11.18.pdf }}</ref>。

== 功能 ==
Z-Library容許用戶自行上傳書籍<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zh.b-ok.global/faq.php|title=FAQ|accessdate=2021-02-13|work=Z-Library}}</ref>，並設立了捐款渠道予人捐款<ref name="Kill time">{{cite news|title=Kill time, not joy: How to be happy at home during the outbreak|url=https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2020/03/20/kill-time-not-joy-how-to-be-happy-at-home-during-the-outbreak.html|date=2020-03-20|accessdate=2021-02-13|work=The Jakarta Post|archive-date=2021-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226221101/https://www.thejakartapost.com/life/2020/03/20/kill-time-not-joy-how-to-be-happy-at-home-during-the-outbreak.html}}</ref>。在網站上用戶可免費下載書籍和期刊<ref name="Kill time"/>。用戶可在不用註冊的情況下下載資源，但下載數量和速度都會較註冊者為低。註冊者可在捐款後享有更多的功能，而且下載數量和速度都會較沒捐款時放寬。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://zh.b-ok.global/profile.php|title=你的個人空間|accessdate=2021-02-13|work=Z-Library}}（需要註冊）</ref>

